colorFillAlertWarning.comment: Fill color to be used behind white warning icon.

colorFillAlertSuccess.comment: Fill color to be used behind white success icon.

colorBackgroundDefault.comment: Default background color that should be applied to all pages other than login and dashboard pages.

colorBackgroundAlertWarning.comment: Background color for warning alerts and notifications.

colorFillAlertNeutral.comment: Fill color to be used behind white neutral/information icon.

colorFillAlertError.comment: Fill color to be used behind white error icon.

colorBackgroundAlertDefault.comment: Background color for default alerts and notifications.

colorBackgroundAlertSuccess.comment: Background color for success alerts and notifications.

colorBackgroundAlertNeutral.comment: Background color for neutral alerts and notifications.

colorBackgroundAlertError.comment: Background color for error alerts and notifications.

borderWidthThin.comment: Border width tokens should only be used within the border property.

borderWidthThick.comment: Border width tokens should only be used within the border property.

borderWidthThicker.comment: Border width tokens should only be used within the border property.

borderWidthThickest.comment: Border width tokens should only be used within the border property.

colorBorderGlobalFocus.comment: Global focus color for better accessibility.

colorBorderAlertSuccess.comment: Border color for success alerts and notifications.

colorBorderAlertWarning.comment: Border color for success alerts and notifications.

colorBorderAlertNeutral.comment: Border color for success alerts and notifications.

colorBorderAlertError.comment: Border color for success alerts and notifications.

borderRadiusReset.comment: Generic reset border radius for global use.

borderRadiusCircle.comment: Circle border radius for global use.

borderRadiusXSmall.comment: Generic extra small border radius value.

borderRadiusXLarge.comment: Generic extra large border radius value.

heightFluid.comment: Height used to span the entire height of its children.

widthFluid.comment: Width used to span the entirety of its parent container.

widthInputFields.comment: Width of input fields that are not full width.

paddingTextField.comment: Padding around TextField, DatePicker, and TimePicker component inputs.

colorTextAlertWarning.comment: Text color for warning and draft notifications.

colorTextAlertNeutral.comment: Text color for hint, neutral and pending notifications.

colorTextAlertError.comment: Text color for error and failure notifications.
